{"tid":989432,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁多人中意舊日本帝國","createTime":"2019-01-21T00:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T10:36:53.000Z","uid":202301,"like":31,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5b70cb4756d1ccc9a8c5257bdc0540fe8eb7376f","tid":989432,"uid":202301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T00:21:47.000Z","msg":"你哋最憎嘅中共係畀日本帝國間接養大嘅，冇日本入侵中國，共產黨一定畀國民黨收皮。<br />\n<br />\n論型棍更加講唔通，海軍制服還可以，陸軍真係柒到老母都唔認得，同時期仿德風嘅國軍制服仲好睇過日軍<br />\n<br />\n論軍紀，同蘇軍一樣咁仆街，喺佔領區姦淫擄掠<br />\n<br />\n用軸心國立場睇日本更加覺得日本仲仆街過意大利。唔係日本拖埋美國落水，打蘇聯嗰陣人哋遠東幾乎冇人咁濟，日本竟然係食花生。日本唔做on9隊友嘅話德國冇可能會輸<br />\n<br />\n有冇日本帝國打手講下點解你哋咁中意日本帝國<br />\n<br />\n利申好中意而家嘅日本，因為日本帝國&ne;而家嘅日本國"},{"pid":"d52d74f78641f6b5eb723415a8cbd819696916e8","tid":989432,"uid":55177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7dfb1e384bd861793832c0ceafada4127f66843","tid":989432,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:06:54.000Z","msg":"日本帝國&ne;而家嘅日本國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係日本帝國個天皇係今上天皇個老豆"},{"pid":"d38c5a661a3c7f1b01e919131c5fa2ea7d12c554","tid":989432,"uid":78574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7dfb1e384bd861793832c0ceafada4127f66843","tid":989432,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:06:54.000Z","msg":"日本帝國&ne;而家嘅日本國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係日本帝國個天皇係今上天皇個老豆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:08:00.000Z","msg":"而家個天皇仲有無權力"},{"pid":"9c6a83365355c4cb40a17b29d197667cd62291e6","tid":989432,"uid":2023